00049   void VRawADCValueProcessor::init() 
00050   {
00051     // --- register conditions data handler
00052     
00053     std::stringstream message;
00054     message << "VRawADCValueProcessor::init> no conditions data handler for the collections:";
00055     bool error=false;
00056     if (!marlin::ConditionsProcessor::registerChangeListener( &_moduleLocationChange ,_colNameModuleLocation)) {
00057       message << " " << _colNameModuleLocation;
00058       error=true;
00059     }
00060 
00061     if (!marlin::ConditionsProcessor::registerChangeListener( &_moduleConnectionChange , _colNameModuleConnection)) {
00062       message << " " << _colNameModuleConnection;
00063       error=true;
00064     }
00065 
00066     if (!marlin::ConditionsProcessor::registerChangeListener( &_moduleTypeChange ,_colNameModuleDescription) ) {
00067       message << " " << _colNameModuleDescription;
00068       error=true;
00069     }
00070 
00071     if(_colNameStageCollection != "StageCollectionNotDefined") {
00072       if (!marlin::ConditionsProcessor::registerChangeListener( &_stagePositionChange ,_colNameStageCollection) ) {
00073         message << " " << _colNameStageCollection;
00074         error=true;
00075       }
00076     }
00077 
00078 
00079     if (error) { 
00080       message <<  ".";
00081       throw ErrorMissingConditionsDataHandler(message.str());
00082     }
00083        
00084     _mapping.init();
00085 
00086     // correct the wrong order of the cells in the A-Hcal description data.
00087     struct tm wrong_order_till;
00088     wrong_order_till.tm_min=0;
00089     wrong_order_till.tm_sec=0;
00090     wrong_order_till.tm_hour=0;
00091     wrong_order_till.tm_wday=0;
00092     wrong_order_till.tm_yday=0;
00093     wrong_order_till.tm_isdst=0;
00094     wrong_order_till.tm_mon=10;
00095     wrong_order_till.tm_mday=26;
00096     wrong_order_till.tm_year=2006-1900;
00097 
00098     _wrongOrderTill=mktime(&wrong_order_till);
00099   }

00115   void VRawADCValueProcessor::correctModuleDescriptionOrder(LCCollection *colP)
00116   {
00117     assert(colP);
00118     std::vector<std::string> insertion_time;
00119     colP->getParameters().getStringVals("DBInsertionTime",insertion_time);
00120     assert(insertion_time.size()>0);
00121     if (insertion_time[0].size()>9) {
00122       insertion_time[0].erase(insertion_time[0].size()-9);
00123     }
00124     unsigned int timestamp=atoi(insertion_time[0].c_str());
00125     double a=timestamp;
00126     double b=_wrongOrderTill;
00127     std::string map_key("MappingCorrected");
00128     std::cout << "time since order was corrected : " << (a-b)/(24*3600.)  << std::endl;
00129     if (timestamp<_wrongOrderTill && colP->getParameters().getIntVal(map_key)!=1) {
00130       for (unsigned int elm_i=0; elm_i<static_cast<unsigned int>(colP->getNumberOfElements()); elm_i++) {
00131         CALICE::ModuleDescription description(colP->getElementAt(elm_i));
00132         //CRP Taken out since we're still using old ModuleDescription 
00133         //Might be re-enabled later on
00134         //if (description.hasCellDimensionsPerCell()) continue;
00135         if (description.getModuleType()>=4 && description.getModuleType()<=7) {
00136           std::string folder_name;
00137           folder_name = colP->getParameters().getStringVal("DBFolder");
00138           std::cout << "flip mapping : " << folder_name << std::endl;
00139           std::vector<CellPar_t> cell_buffer;
00140           cell_buffer.resize(description.getNCells());
00141           UInt_t n_lines=(description.getNCells()>=216  ? 12 : 6);
00142           for (unsigned int cell_i=0; cell_i<description.getNCells(); cell_i++) {
00143             unsigned int new_cell_i=(cell_i%18)*n_lines+cell_i/18;
00144             assert(new_cell_i < description.getNCells());
00145             cell_buffer[new_cell_i]=CellPar_t(description.getCellXPos(cell_i),
00146                                               description.getCellYPos(cell_i),
00147                                               description.getGeometricalCellIndex(cell_i));
00148           }
00149           for (unsigned int new_cell_i=0; new_cell_i<description.getNCells(); new_cell_i++) {
00150             description.setCellXPos(new_cell_i,cell_buffer[new_cell_i].posX());
00151             description.setCellYPos(new_cell_i,cell_buffer[new_cell_i].posY());
00152             description.setGeometricalCellIndex(new_cell_i,cell_buffer[new_cell_i].index());
00153           }
00154         }
00155       }
00156       colP->parameters().setValue(map_key,static_cast<int>(1));
00157 
00158     }
00159     
00160   }
